## After fresh local clone:
npm install -g hexo-cli
npm install
git clone https://github.com/ets/hexo-theme-icarus.git themes/icarus
cd themes/icarus
git co origin/ericsimmerman-blog
cd ../..
hexo generate


## If you want to run a dev server locally
npm install hexo-server --save


## View a local update

hexo server
hexo deploy